6:
That smooth talkin' bastard... I
thought this'd be important, but
we're just runnin' more of his errands!
9:
Heh. Or maybe you're just
pretending to be tricked by him
every time—it's a cute thing you two
have going.
14: Huh?! I ain't pretendin' to do—
20:
Ohmygosh, Whitetail!
It's you! I can't believe my eyes!
28:
Oh! My apologies.
My name is Sven!
31:
Hearing the legends of Whitetail
inspired me to go on my own
journey and travel the world!
35:
Are you not familiar with the
legends?
They're all in this book! Please, have
a look!
39:
The Return... of... Whitetail?
What kind of nonsense in this?
43:
This is definitely about you, Nimbus.
Though certain parts have clearly
been... embellished.
52:
Curious, look at the last page. It says
it's edited by Claudius Navelle.
62:
When I read this book I made up my
mind—I want to become strong and
cool, just like you!
64:
So please, Whitetail!
Please make me your apprentice!
76:
Listen here, pipsqueak. Let's get a
few things straight.
I. Am. Not. Whitetail. I—
87:
Ohmygosh... am I dreaming? The
great Whitetail himself is fighting to
save ME!
90:
If I'm gonna be like him, I need to
prove that I'm strong too!
Here I come!
94: This little mouse isn't half bad!
98:
How did I do, Whitetail? Did you see
me there? I gave it my all!
122:
Stop movin'. Those are some serious
wounds. Why'd you have to go and
do somethin' so stupid, huh?
124:
And just to be clear: I'm not
Whitetail.
When your wounds heal, I want you
outta here.
126:
What do you mean you're not
Whitetail? Look at you! Who else
could you be?
127:
You're the hero who put an end to
the war between the catfolk and
dogfolk.
130:
That wasn't me.
That was these guys here.
135:
Sven, was it? You're one of the
mousefolk, are you not?
Why do you look up to Whitetail so?
139:
Everyone always told me the war
had nothing to do with us mice.
But I don't know...
140:
I always had this feeling that we
mousefolk would get swept up in it
too one day. I wanted to be ready
for that! To fight!
143:
But then the war went and
ended—well, YOU put an end to it,
Whitetail! It was unthinkable!
144:
You inspired me and countless
others.
That's why I want to become just like
you!
148:
So you left your home and went on
a journey alone? That's pretty brave.
152:
So, please, Whitetail! I beg you!
Make me your apprentice!
158: Goddamn it, kid, I told you...
162:
Gah. Fine. If you've come this far, I
guess there's no stoppin' ya.
167:
Indeed.
Welcome to Starview Village, Sven.
We're glad to have you on the team.
175:
All right, Sven. Let's get a few things
straight.
178:
I'm not Whitetail. You sure you're
okay with that? Don't do anything
you'll regret later.
181:
Y-yes. I understand, Wh—
I mean, uh...
189:
Nimbus! I understand completely,
Master Nimbus!
